{"id":5592,"date":"2015-09-01T06:45:51","date_gmt":"2015-09-01T06:45:51","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/ezrankings.org\/blog\/?p=3588"},"modified":"2022-11-21T11:47:16","modified_gmt":"2022-11-21T11:47:16","slug":"5-tips-for-creating-engaging-content-on-social-media-platforms","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"\/blog\/5-tips-for-creating-engaging-content-on-social-media-platforms\/","title":{"rendered":"5 Tips for Creating Engaging Content on Social Media Platforms"},"content":{"rendered":"<div id=\"attachment_10720\" style=\"width: 680px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-10720\" class=\"size-full wp-image-10720\" src=\"https:\/\/ezranking.s3.eu-west-2.amazonaws.com\/ezrankings\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/09\/07123508\/create-more-engaging-content.jpg\" alt=\"Source - Miller Media\" width=\"670\" height=\"400\" srcset=\"https:\/\/ezranking.s3.eu-west-2.amazonaws.com\/ezrankings\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/09\/07123508\/create-more-engaging-content.jpg 670w, https:\/\/ezranking.s3.eu-west-2.amazonaws.com\/ezrankings\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2015\/09\/07123508\/create-more-engaging-content-300x179.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 670px) 100vw, 670px\" \/><p id=\"caption-attachment-10720\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Source &#8211;<br \/>Miller Media<\/p><\/div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\" align=\"justify\">The type of content you upload on social media platforms will have a direct effect on the level of engagement with your target audience. So, you need to generate more interesting and <a class=\"ezurl\" href=\"\/blog\/5-tips-for-creating-engaging-content-on-social-media-platforms\/\">useful content for maximum social media engagement<\/a> and interaction. Since all <a class=\"ezurl\" href=\"https:\/\/www.ezrankings.com\/social-media-marketing-services.html\"><strong>social media<\/strong><\/a> generate signals that among other things positively affect SEO performance, it is important that you invest some time and effort to create quality content that would attract maximum attention.<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Identify Your Target Group<\/li>\n<li>Type and Time<\/li>\n<li>Stay Updated<\/li>\n<li>Familiarity<\/li>\n<li>Employee Participation<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_69 counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-grey ez-toc-container-direction\">\n<div class=\"ez-toc-title-container\">\n<p class=\"ez-toc-title \" >Table of Contents<\/p>\n<span class=\"ez-toc-title-toggle\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn-xs ez-toc-btn-default ez-toc-toggle\" aria-label=\"Toggle Table of Content\"><span class=\"ez-toc-js-icon-con\"><span class=\"\"><span class=\"eztoc-hide\" style=\"display:none;\">Toggle<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-icon-toggle-span\"><svg style=\"fill: #999;color:#999\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" class=\"list-377408\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M6 6H4v2h2V6zm14 0H8v2h12V6zM4 11h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2zM4 16h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2z\" fill=\"currentColor\"><\/path><\/svg><svg style=\"fill: #999;color:#999\" class=\"arrow-unsorted-368013\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" version=\"1.2\" baseProfile=\"tiny\"><path d=\"M18.2 9.3l-6.2-6.3-6.2 6.3c-.2.2-.3.4-.3.7s.1.5.3.7c.2.2.4.3.7.3h11c.3 0 .5-.1.7-.3.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7zM5.8 14.7l6.2 6.3 6.2-6.3c.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7c-.2-.2-.4-.3-.7-.3h-11c-.3 0-.5.1-.7.3-.2.2-.3.5-.3.7s.1.5.3.7z\"\/><\/svg><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/a><\/span><\/div>\n<nav><ul class='ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1 ' ><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"\/blog\/5-tips-for-creating-engaging-content-on-social-media-platforms\/#1_Identify_Your_Target_Group\" title=\"1. Identify Your Target Group\">1. Identify Your Target Group<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"\/blog\/5-tips-for-creating-engaging-content-on-social-media-platforms\/#2_Type_and_Time\" title=\"2. Type and Time\">2. Type and Time<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"\/blog\/5-tips-for-creating-engaging-content-on-social-media-platforms\/#3_Stay_Updated\" title=\"3. Stay Updated\">3. Stay Updated<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"\/blog\/5-tips-for-creating-engaging-content-on-social-media-platforms\/#4_Familiarity\" title=\"4. Familiarity\">4. Familiarity<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5\" href=\"\/blog\/5-tips-for-creating-engaging-content-on-social-media-platforms\/#5_Employee_Participation\" title=\"5. Employee Participation\">5. Employee Participation<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"1_Identify_Your_Target_Group\"><\/span>1. Identify Your Target Group<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\" align=\"justify\">Try doing some research on who is your target audience and groups on social media. For example, does Facebook engage the same type of audience as Twitter? What are the major demographic groups that are engaged in each social media platform? Based on the gathered data, you will be able to customize your content to match with specific audience groups for better engagement.<\/p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"2_Type_and_Time\"><\/span>2. Type and Time<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\" align=\"justify\">You must focus on the type of content that you post. For example, visual and interactive media work best in platforms such as Facebook whereas more question and answer type content works best on Twitter. You can use infographics, quotes, behind scene photos, links, questions, and more to maximize likes, shares and re-tweets.<\/p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"3_Stay_Updated\"><\/span>3. Stay Updated<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\" align=\"justify\">Follow the recent trends and news related to your brand and your company goals. Your audience wants to know that you are updated as well and that you are following the flow of information.<\/p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"4_Familiarity\"><\/span>4. Familiarity<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\" align=\"justify\">You want your audience to feel comfortable and familiar with your brand. One of the best ways to do so is by being steady when it comes to the flow of your postings and uploaded information.<\/p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"5_Employee_Participation\"><\/span>5. Employee Participation<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\" align=\"justify\">Encourage your employees to interact with all your current and potential customers through their professional <a href=\"\/blog\/how-to-do-facebook-lead-ads-a-step-by-step-guide\/\">Facebook<\/a> and Twitter accounts. This will show your customers the actual value of the brand and its services.<\/p>\n<p align=\"justify\">For any queries, Connect with EZ Rankings &#8211; <a href=\"https:\/\/www.ezrankings.com\/\">Digital Marketing Company<\/a>!<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>The type of content you upload on social media platforms will have a direct effect on the level of engagement with your target audience. So, you need to generate more interesting and useful content for maximum social media engagement and interaction. Since all social media generate signals that among other things positively affect SEO performance, [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":3655,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[3],"tags":[185,184],"class_list":["post-5592","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-smo","tag-content-generating","tag-engaging-content"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"\/blog\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/5592"}],"collection":[{"href":"\/blog\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"\/blog\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"\/blog\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"\/blog\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=5592"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"\/blog\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/5592\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"\/blog\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/3655"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"\/blog\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=5592"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"\/blog\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=5592"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"\/blog\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=5592"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}